like it might have worked,

00:14:34.220 --> 00:14:36.760
but the actual ember,
the one that was still burning,

00:14:36.760 --> 00:14:40.280
that was about just this tiny
little glowing orange spot,

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:43.902
and that's what we got to catch
and grow into all of the bark

00:14:43.902 --> 00:14:46.500
