that it's still surviving.

00:14:55.200 --> 00:14:56.955
So long as you can see smoke,

00:14:56.955 --> 00:14:59.648
chances are you still
probably have a viable ember.

00:14:59.648 --> 00:15:01.750
You still just need
to transfer it over,

00:15:01.750 --> 00:15:03.422
